{
  "stem": "2906.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was, in Kielce-- I think in Kielce it was it-- that they came in a kibbutz, and they killed, while-- I think were two of the young people in the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This of-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we always have to be on guard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was always, at night, always boys to go around with a-- with a rifle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was 500 people there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think there was maybe 40 girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The rest was boys.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we worked, but they didn't give us-- you know, they didn't give us what we-- they gave us a-- a bread.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, take a hike and heck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It so, so hard, You know, some others stole the money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know whatever they did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was organized from Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the people who were there, they-- they wasn't very-- very honest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at night, they told us to be-- yes, the-- the police were watching us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, and the police wasn't-- didn't kill though.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing, people-- that we were afraid, because we find over there they killed in the Kibbutz, but two of the four of the people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they told us every-- every girl, where she stays.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had like-- they made with us, every time, we should be ready.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "These girls stays with these boys, these girls stay with these boys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they told us, in case something happened, everybody should be quiet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, a boy who-- who had the-- this rifle and accidentally shoot out, the rifle shoot out at him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we thought that the-- they coming to kill us!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what did the girls do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They started screaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We were supposed to be-- told to be quiet, but instead quiet, they screamed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, thank God it was OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
